Sorry, this is my first Pirate Bay upload, so the Description should be: 

"Buscemi - Complete Discography 1998-2011"

Includes following albums:
- Mocha Supremo [1998]
- Our Girl in Havana [2001]
- A Warm Blue Note Session [2001]
- Calmino Real [2003]
- Caliente! (Blue Note) [2004]
- Late Nite Reworks Vol. 1 (A collection of Remixes by Buscemi) [2005]
- Retro Nuevo [2006]
- Welcome to the Party Vol.1 (Squadra Bossa ft. Buscemi) [2008]
- Jazz Works (w. The Michel Bisceglia Ensemble) [2008]
- Vertov Luomo Con La Macchina Da Presa (w. The Michel Bisceglia Ensemble) [2009]
- Rocco con Buscemi (w. Rocco Granata) [2011]
